Package: ShieldAIRR
Title: TCR/BCR AIRR Repertoire Analysis Toolkit
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("XF", "Zhang", email = "cheungxuefei@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    High-level helpers for AIRR-style TCR/BCR repertoires, including
    CDR3 physicochemical landscape, V/J gene usage, clonal diversity,
    time-series trajectory clustering, and bulk V/J differential analysis.
